!! The Plugin

The [[EditButtons|$:/plugins/telmiger/EditButtons]] plugin makes editing of tiddlers more efficient by adding three buttons to the ''edit toolbar'': 

* Cancel & Close (Discard & Close)
* Save & Close (Done & Close)
* Save & Keep Open (Done & Reopen)

Inspired by Josiah and Richard William Smith. See Discussion in the [[Google Group|https://groups.google.com/d/msg/tiddlywiki/A4v-DqjN_D8/4hkOaaf0BQAJ]].

